title: The Algerian War 1954-1962
description:
5 episode (in 3 DVDs) documentary to mark the 50th anniversary of that momentous struggle.

Episode 1 - Road to Rebllion 
(DVD 1 - Roots of War 1830-1955)

Episode 2 -  A Question of Conscience 
(DVD 2 - Crisis in France - The Return of De Gaulle 1956-1960)

Episode 3 - I Understand You 
(DVD 2 - Crisis in France - The Return of De Gaulle 1956-1960)

Episode 4 - To the Barricades 
(DVD 3 - The Final Showdown, 1960-1962)

Episode 5 - The Suitcase or the Coffin 
(DVD 3 - The Final Showdown, 1960-1962)

Bonus - America Salutes Algerian Independence 
(DVD 1 - Roots of War 1830-1955)
